  // ============================================================================
  // SPECIAL ZOMBIE CLASSES  (Mother Zombie, Nemesis, Assassin)
  // ============================================================================
  //
  //  Each entry defines a special zombie role.
  //  Name must match the NemesisNames / AssassinNames / MotherZombieNames
  //  strings set in the game-mode blocks above.
  //
  //  Stats fields:
  //    Health             -- base HP (used when the mode health override is 0).
  //    MotherZombieHealth -- HP when acting as a mother zombie.
  //    Speed              -- movement speed multiplier (1.0 = default CS2 speed).
  //    Damage             -- knife damage per hit.
  //    Gravity            -- gravity multiplier (0.5 = floaty / low-gravity jumps).
  //    Fov                -- field of view in degrees.
  //    EnableRegen        -- true = health regeneration is active.
  //    HpRegenSec         -- regeneration interval in seconds.
  //    HpRegenHp          -- HP restored per interval.
  //    ZombieSoundVolume  -- volume of zombie sounds (0.0-1.0).
  //    IdleInterval       -- average seconds between idle sound plays.
  //
